description: Skåne-möllan AB engages in the production and marketing of flour and cereal products for the food industry. Its main products include: Bakery Wheat flours, such as Northern Spring, Wheat flour for Pizza and Expert Wheat flour, among others; Bakery Coarse products, such as Crushed Wheat, Extra Fine Cross milled and Crushed Rye, among others, Bakery Rye flours, such as Sifted Rye Flour 000, Sifted Bakery flour and Rye flour S, among others, and Organic flour, such as The Millers Organic Wheat flour, Organic Rye flour S and Organic Bakery Wheat flour UA. The firm offers household flour under the brand name Mollarens. Additionally, the Company offers heat treated products, which are gathered under the name TTT. As of December 31, 2011, the Company had two wholly owned subsidiaries, Svalof Food AB and TTT GmbH, as well as two affiliates, including Vallakra Lantmannaaffar AB and Mel-Compagniet ApS.
